import { Route, Switch } from "react-router-dom"
import { Header, Sidebar } from "../../Components"
import Home from "../Home/Home"

const Layout = () => {
    return(
        <>
            <Header />
            <Sidebar />
            <Switch>
                <Route path={"/"} component={Home} />

            </Switch>
        </>
    )
}

export default Layout
